Stop Doing Tutorials. Learn Programming Like This--Learn programming faster and better

Krishna Sree 24-09-2024 18:04

If I had to start learning Python again, I would do it differently.Back when I was a Psychology undergraduate student, I started studying Python with Coursera’s courses. I watched and rewatched videos until I gained some familiarity, fluency, and understanding of the concepts.“I learned Python, yay!” I thought.Well, not really. When I took my first programming test, I realized I didn’t know how to code. I stared at the computer trying to figure out how to start writing the first few lines.This is the modern illusion of learning.
